item.title: 2023-04-08: Astronaut Kayaking
item.description: An astronaut took to the lake, In a kayak for leisure’s sweet sake, In zero G style, It floated a while, A space-kayak trip, quite opaque.

item.title: 2023-04-08: Bee Hiking
item.description: A bee buzzed along on a hike, Through flowers and meadows alike, It gathered sweet nectar, A floral collector, A pollinating journey on strike.

item.title: 2023-04-08: Ninja Yoga
item.description: A ninja found peace in a pose, With yoga, a calm juxtapose, In silence and stealth, A focus of wealth, A warrior’s zen state, it shows.

item.title: Dolphin Kayaking
item.description: A dolphin decided to glide, In a kayak, a new way to ride, With fins as its guide, The boat gently glides, A maritime trip so bona fide.

item.title: Kangaroo Yoga
item.description: A kangaroo tried out some yoga, Its balance, quite like a tightrope-a, With a hop and a stretch, It found quite the fetch, A marsupial zen-like persona.

item.title: Raccoon Hiking
item.description: A raccoon set off for a hike, With a backpack and walking stick-like, Through forests it strolled, With snacks to unfold, Its trail mix, a balanced delight.
